了“One Guitar”，并与 Joe Grushecky 和 ​​Houserockers 一起演奏了“Never Be Enough Time”。</p><p>随后，他继续演奏了一系列自己的热门歌曲，包括《城镇边缘的黑暗》、《应许之地》、《粉红凯迪拉克》，以及他为琼·杰特创作的与该活动同名的《Light Of Day》和迈克尔·J·福克斯 1987 年的同名电影。看看下面的视频。 </p><p><iframe title="杰西·马林 (Jesse Malin) ft. 布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 (Bruce Springsteen) - 现场 |损坏的收音机 - LOD 25 @ Count Basie, Red Bank NJ 1/18/25" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ucy_O9lXdh8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe title="布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀和威利·尼罗 - 一把吉他" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/wkqBwp3M1-s?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 - 现场 |黑暗 - 白天之光 2025 @ Count Basie Theater, Red Bank NJ 1/18/25" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/w46qIfynY7Q?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 - 现场 | Savin’ Up - Light of Day 2025 @ Count Basie Theater, Red Bank NJ 1/18/25" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UDmFzpYEENs?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Pumping Iron- Bruce Springsteen Joe Grushecky The Houserockers - Light Of Day 2025" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KgYN3LdH8b8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 - 现场 |粉色凯迪拉克 - Light of Day 2025 @ Count Basie, Red Bank NJ 1/18/25" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Fpu_P0rmmx4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀《日光之光》祝鲍勃和布鲁斯生日快乐，把鼻子伸进蛋糕里" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gnkHffT-lMk?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 - 现场 | Thunder Road - Light of Day 2025 @ Count Basie, Red Bank NJ 1/18/25" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/F2pOQif97zs?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀的其他新闻中，2025 年他将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-extends-2025-tour-with-dates-in-manchester-and-liverpool-3798567">与 E Street Band 一起扩展他的全球巡演</a>，其中包括整个 7 月份在英国和欧洲各个城市的演出。请在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-teases-never-before-released-material-ahead-of-born-to-run-50th-anniversary-3824142">此处</a>查看完整的日期列表并<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fbruce-springsteen-and-the-e-street-band-tickets%2Farti