iritbox@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spiritbox">Spiritbox</a>宣布举办慈善抽奖活动，以支持<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">洛杉矶野火</a>的受害者 - 了解更多信息如下。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/spiritbox-eternal-blue-interview-3474802">Spiritbox：“我们的粉丝正在接受改变——我们仍在摸索自己”</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周末（1 月 18 日），这支加拿大金属乐队在社交媒体上分享说，他们发起了一场慈善抽奖活动，为那些受到早些时候席卷加州的毁灭性洛杉矶山火影响的人们“筹集尽可能多的资金来帮助”本月。</p><p>自1月7日山火爆发以来，洛杉矶已有超过15万居民被迫撤离家园。迄今为止， <a href="https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/california-wildfires-what-we-know-victims-killed-rcna188240" target="_blank" rel="noopener">已报告 27 人确认死亡</a>，另有 20 多人失踪。</p><p> Spiritbox 的慈善抽奖活动由吉他手迈克·斯金格 (Mike Stringer) 主持，他在社交媒体上写道：“南加州在过去的一个半星期里面临着毁灭性的山火，我不仅想捐款，还想尽力筹集尽可能多的资金来提供帮助。目睹破坏及其影响令人心碎。” </p><figure id="attachment_3830241" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3830241" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3830241" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/spiritbox-josh-gilbert@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/spiritbox-josh-gilbert@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/spiritbox-josh-gilbert@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/spiritbox-josh-gilbert@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/spiritbox-josh-gilbert@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/spiritbox-josh-gilbert@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/spiritbox-josh-gilbert@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3830241" class="wp-caption-text"> Spiritbox 的乔什·吉尔伯特。图片来源：Katja Ogrin/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p>斯金格补充说，野火也影响了乐队，贝斯手乔什·吉尔伯特在这场灾难中失去了家。抽奖的大奖包括斯金格在路上或录音室使用过的一系列电吉他、踏板和扩音器。</p><p>每次参加抽奖的费用为 20 美元。所有收益将直接捐给大洛杉矶仁人家园和阿尔塔迪纳青少年女孩火灾恢复组织 - <a href="https://riserecords.com/collections/artist-spiritbox/products/sptbraff00-dd" target="_blank" rel="noopener">要了解更多信息并参加抽奖，请点击此处</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DE8LqoJzNNQ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.