查看他们 2025 年巡演日期的完整列表</a>。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/motorheads-mikkey-dee-almost-died-from-sepsis-and-was-nearly-playing-drums-with-lemmy-in-heaven-3825681"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>在其他新闻中，最近有报道称，已故 Motörhead 主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lemmys-ashes-to-go-on-display-at-stringfellows-strip-club-in-london-he-loved-the-rocknroll-spirit-and-he-certainly-loved-the-view-3816801">Lemmy 的一些骨灰将在伦敦 Stringfellow 脱衣舞俱乐部永久展出</a>。该网站由已故商人兼夜总会老板 Peter Stringfellow 创建，也是 Motörhead 主唱的热门目的地。</p><p>莱米早在 2016 年就透露了他对俱乐部的喜爱，当时他告诉<em><a href="https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=92X1567220&amp;xcust=loudersound_gb_1272568857427877028&amp;xs=1&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fthehollywoodtimesdotorg.wordpress.com%2Fauthor%2Ftht2016%2Fpage%2F33%2F&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.loudersound.com%2Fnews%2Fhe-loved-the-rocknroll-spirit-and-he-certainly-loved-the-view-more-of-lemmys-ashes-have-found-a-final-home-at-a-famous-strip-club-in-london" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《好莱坞时报》</a></em> ，当他不在客场时，他很喜欢在那里度过时光。 “伦敦的 Stringfellows……这是一家高端脱衣舞俱乐部。那里总是受到热烈的欢迎。我从 1964 年起就认识店主 Peter，”他说。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/scorpions-postpone-las-vegas-residency-for-drummer-mikkey-dee-to-recover-from-illness-3830232">蝎子乐队推迟鼓手 Mikkey Dee 因病康复而推迟在拉斯维加斯驻场的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
