酒店出租一​​周，为逃离山火的 50 个家庭提供庇护</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3827798" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827798" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827798" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA-Wildfires.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA-Wildfires.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA-Wildfires-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA-Wildfires-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA-Wildfires-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA-Wildfires-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/LA-Wildfires-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827798" class="wp-caption-text">洛杉矶日落大道的野火（图片来源：Apu Gomes/Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-urges-brands-gifting-her-clothing-to-instead-donate-it-to-those-affected-by-horrific-la-wildfires-3828185">Charli XCX 呼吁品牌赠送她的衣服“将它们送给真正需要它的人”。</a>随后，她分享了造型师 Lana Jay Lackey 组织的衣物捐赠活动的细节，并敦促其他人与她一起捐赠。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">阿丽亚娜·格兰德 (Ariana Grande)</a> 、比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish) 等人<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">对野火造成的“令人心碎”的破坏做出了反应</a>，为需要帮助的人分享资源链接。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/la-music-community-tragic-wildfires-long-lasting-effects-3828259">洛杉矶音乐界的成员也向<i>《NME》</i>表示，他们受到了严重打击</a>，许多场馆、工作室和艺术家都受到了火灾的影响。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-joins-fireaid-benefit-concert-for-la-wildfire-relief-3830217">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo) 参加洛杉矶野火救援 FireAid 慈善音乐会</a>后，首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发表。</p> ;
